methods.commentText:
Returns the getCategory of the error.

Errors come in 2 categories: FATAL, RECOVERABLE

FATAL: The session cannot be recovered and needs to be re-created. A likely cause is that the User does not have access to this Realm. Check that the {@link SyncConfiguration} is correct.

RECOVERABLE: Temporary error. The session will automatically try to recover as soon as possible.
